{"article_id": "M.1436026176.A.4E1", "article_title": "[問題] 台大財金vs港中大會計", "author": "rabbithsu (兔)", "board": "SeniorHigh", "content": "各位好 我是今年高三生 正在面臨校系抉擇 台大財金vs港中大會計 先簡述自己想去香港的原因 1.英文不好想去加強 2.想去看看這個世界 3.香港薪水高 可是面臨幾個阻力 1.香港4年大約要300萬，可是獎學金只有40萬NT.... 我家經濟狀況不優，可能要借錢去念 2.會計系在香港待遇似乎不如finIB的學生 由於實在有點猶豫不決 想聽聽各位的意見~ 1.如果是各位，會怎麼選擇? 2.台灣金融業VS香港會計業 哪邊待遇平均比較好? 3.如果選擇香港，大概多久可以回本? 謝謝 ", "date": "Sun Jul  5 00:09:33 2015", "ip": "59.115.47.98", "message_count": {"all": 41, "boo": 2, "count": 19, "neutral": 18, "push": 21}, "messages": [{"push_content": "香港薪水高....也要看你的造化吧......", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:15", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "yuxiang"}, {"push_content": "好困難的問題，不太知道欸  請神人回答XD", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:16", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "hareusagi"}, {"push_content": "經濟不允許就台大吧", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:18", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Zw111196"}, {"push_content": "我學長去年上了港中IB 感覺還不錯", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:18", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "pork6631"}, {"push_content": "雖然薪水高但你什麼時候可以賺回來台港學費中間的價差?", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:20", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Zw111196"}, {"push_content": "之前有學長台大財金唸完跑去LSE唸研究所，畢業國外起薪1", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:23", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Zw111196"}, {"push_content": "20k", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:23", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Zw111196"}, {"push_content": "香港", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:33", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "v2007v2007"}, {"push_content": "台大財金 香港不會廣東話 學費價差很多 那個300萬可", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:35", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "以研究所申請美國的了", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:35", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "等等我是說不會廣東話不方便  跟學費沒有關係", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:35", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "而且之前有在新聞看到香港唸完會計結果還是回來台灣", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "PwC", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:36", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "家裡經濟無法支持 就別去香港", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 00:37", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "jojia"}, {"push_content": "出國讀書有利是基於沒經濟壓力的情況 負債讀書 划不來", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 01:00", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "qq251988"}, {"push_content": "你不要忘記 你出來就要欠債", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 02:27", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "nurais1127"}, {"push_content": "而且物價高生活環境差又髒", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 02:28", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "nurais1127"}, {"push_content": "而且真正能在香港打下一片天的往往都是中國來的...", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 02:29", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "nurais1127"}, {"push_content": "我同學外商銀行上面都是浙大幫的", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 02:29", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "nurais1127"}, {"push_content": "小魯112財金畢 現在在香港當台勞 推台大財金", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 02:44", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "jn8029"}, {"push_content": "香港的會計準則是acca(大英體系跟中國在用的) 證照是hkcpa", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 06:59", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "目前已經供過於求", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 06:59", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "有學長說過港中大幾乎都講廣東話噢 這筆錢乾脆拿去補習", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 07:03", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "然後香港薪水高物價房價也高呀 一份燒鴨沒白飯20港幣 我朋", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 07:04", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "友經濟小康也是住政府配給的屋村", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 07:04", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "其實香港不是每個人英文都很好 中文也爛透惹", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 07:06", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Yozzit"}, {"push_content": "香港", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 07:27", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "Medres"}, {"push_content": "香港", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 09:31", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "buddhawill"}, {"push_content": "去香港英文會變好嗎哈哈哈", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 09:59", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "anderson85"}, {"push_content": "經濟許可再去吧", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 11:17", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "jp9851tw"}, {"push_content": "不管是哪裡來的 只要讀得好都能在香港打下一片天好嗎..", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 11:54", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Rachelmas"}, {"push_content": "真心建議 經濟不允許就別去香港了", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 11:55", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "Rachelmas"}, {"push_content": "家裡經濟狀況不好 別去香港了 去台大吧", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 12:08", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "bye2007"}, {"push_content": "金融板也推你把錢拿去投資歐美研究所比較實際", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 12:34", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "karta1565315"}, {"push_content": "讀台大 將來拿美國全額獎學金(GPA要3.7以上喔)", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 13:26", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "david190"}, {"push_content": "拿到美國名校學歷後 再考慮去哪裡工作", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 13:27", "push_tag": "→", "push_userid": "david190"}, {"push_content": "300萬省下來，台大唸完後去美國就好", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 14:12", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "kazureyesean"}, {"push_content": "是誰說在臺大等我們的", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 14:50", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "wms0919"}, {"push_content": "未來自己決定", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 17:23", "push_tag": "噓", "push_userid": "Kobe2424"}, {"push_content": "david大，財金要拿獎學金我只聽過博士學位耶...", "push_ipdatetime": "07/05 20:38", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "warex14"}, {"push_content": "香港好，香港雖然也不如以往，但還是比台灣好", "push_ipdatetime": "07/06 09:31", "push_tag": "推", "push_userid": "acbwanatha"}], "url": "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/SENIORHIGH/M.1436026176.A.4E1.html"}